<h1>Profile</h1>
<p>Username:<span><input type='text' name='username' value='{{user.username}}'></span></p>
<p>Email:<span><input type='text' name='email' value='{{user.email}}'></span></p>
<p>Password:<span><input type='text' name='password' placeholder='Add new password'></span></p>
<p>add more...<span></span></p>
